--   - layer/core/adapter-pattern.md
--   - layer/core/dependable-rust.md
--   - layer/core/unix-philosophy.md
--   - layer/core/oxidized-knowledge.md
--
-- Core build guidance is implementation governance, not runtime authority.
-- Runtime authority comes from MCT domain facts such as MctPeerBinding,
-- ToyGrant, policy snapshots, and the MctObservation ledger.
